Nigeria’s Attorney General and Minister of Justice,Abubakar Malami, has reacted to reports on his approval of vessels’ auction. The Minister, in a lenghty statement signed by his media aide, Dr Umar Gwandu on Sunday described his approval as legal. Read the AGF’s statement below: VESSELS AUCTION: MY APPROVAL LEGAL – MALAMI Dr. Umar Jibrilu GwanduSpecial Assistant on Media and Public RelationsOffice of the Attorney-General of the Federationand Minister of Justice12th July, 2020